        SELECT DISTINCT
            e.viewpoint_id,
            e.name_primary,
            e.name_variants,
            e.category_norm,
            e.popularity,
            0.0 as name_score,
            1.0 as geo_score,
            0.0 as category_score
        FROM viewpoint_entity e
        WHERE viewpoint_id IN (
                    SELECT DISTINCT viewpoint_id 
                    FROM viewpoint_visual_tags 
                    WHERE tags @> %s::jsonb OR tags @> %s::jsonb
                    AND season = %s
                )
        ORDER BY e.popularity DESC NULLS LAST
        LIMIT %s
        ", "params": ["["cherry_blossom"]", "["blooming_flowers"]", "spring", 50]}]

        SELECT DISTINCT
            e.viewpoint_id,
            e.name_primary,
            e.name_variants,
            e.category_norm,
            e.popularity,
            0.0 as name_score,
            1.0 as geo_score,
            0.0 as category_score
        FROM viewpoint_entity e
        WHERE viewpoint_id IN (
                    SELECT DISTINCT viewpoint_id 
                    FROM viewpoint_visual_tags 
                    WHERE tags @> %s::jsonb OR tags @> %s::jsonb
                    AND season = %s
                )
        ORDER BY e.popularity DESC NULLS LAST
        LIMIT %s
        ", "params": ["["cherry_blossom"]", "["blooming_flowers"]", "spring", 50]}]
